She quickly taken back the receipt as she was afraid i may taken picture of it. Well CCTV wont lie and has already captured i am NOT up for a free lunch because if I am staying @ Harbour Plaza Metropolis what is like to me with your most expensive menu. Good luck and keep it up with the segregation and discrimination as I been place at the service counter and not at the table like what other people do. If the management of this stupid restaurant was reading this please educated your image of the “Japanese Restaurant” even the worker are Hong Kong Chinese. 我的母親也是中國人，7年前在泰國死亡。
my son likes cheese pizza :)

result.name: 梁山泊日本料理

reviews.text: 看似有規模，實質不知所謂，一餐飯入面竟然有幾次出錯🙄； 三文魚茶泡飯竟然冇茶，咖哩豬扒湯麵竟然出咗咖哩豬扒飯， 再次跟進竟然出咗咖哩豬扒泡湯麵🤔
在附近幾年才第一次試，可能位置問題，發現唔到此餐廳，星期日午餐抵食，大部分都係$70樓下，有麵屎湯、茶蒸、沙律、咖啡等，只係樓面人手比較少，服務水平一般，出菜比較慢。
Price is reasonable with different style of food.
鰻魚飯麻麻地，有Ｄ腥
晏晝買4送1，好抵食。
